    <summary>A OneNote add-in with simple, yet powerful and useful features</summary>
    <description>OneMore is an add-in for OneNote with simple and powerful features that make OneNote a better OneNote.</description>
    <releaseNotes>## What's Changed

* Added option to capture anonymous telemetry, [#1974](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1974)
   * User is prompted with one-time splash screen, but it can be turned on or off in Settings
   * Please opt-in to help me improve OneMore!
* Updated Active Setup robustness, [#1963](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1963)
* Fixed an issue where Copy as Text would copy the entire page is only a URL is selected, [#1921](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1921)
* Fixed an issue where PlantUML would fail if containing a URL, [#1967](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1967)
* Fixed an issue Preview Markdown would stop interpreting after a code blocks, [#1979](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1979)
* Fixed(?) an issue where OneNote architecture was not properly detected on AMR64, [#1981](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1981)
* Fixed an issue where copy section group failed to copy to another notebook, [#1990](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1990)

## Experimental
* Added non-indexed full-text search capabilities, bound to `Alt+Shift+G`, [#1856](https://github.com/stevencohn/OneMore/issues/1856)
   * ΓÜá∩╕Å WARNING: this is not fully baked. Needs performance improvements and may cause OneNote to hang upon exit
   * Only available after enabling the _Experimental_ option

## Internal Updates
* Updated build.ps1 to allow VS2026

